            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeTags",
                    "id": "147e57b4-1c27-48bc-ac89-e59f9e92a7f5",
                    "scope": "scene",
                    "scopeId": "f1d169df-e10e-451d-8481-0d0290b7cbbe",
                    "scopeFilterId": null,
                    "tagsToAdd": "hadMissingStudent",
                    "tagsToRemove": null
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.branch",
                    "sections": [
                        {
                            "type": "nodes.branchSection",
                            "expression": {
                                "type": "expressions.and",
                                "left": {
                                    "type": "expressions.inTags",
                                    "scope": "actor",
                                    "scopeId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "scopeFilterId": null,
                                    "tags": "TalkedWraith",
                                    "has": true
                                },
                                "right": {
                                    "type": "expressions.variableComparison",
                                    "variableScope": "global",
                                    "variableName": "time.day",
                                    "operator": "eq",
                                    "compareTo": "32",
                                    "sceneId": "f1d169df-e10e-451d-8481-0d0290b7cbbe",
                                    "propId": null
                                }
                            },
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "973a1068-9eba-4462-8a65-49ee72c31000",
                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Is Joel still alive then?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "1",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "9c14784a-7af9-46d3-b514-6800925aa499",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Silvia says he is, but the Wraith's magic is blocking her spells. I will have to confront the Wraith directly.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "1",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "4c1e1f0a-5ee0-4fda-ba98-5be18624db7a",
                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Then why are you not doing that now instead of standing here? The boy might not survive!",
                                    "emotion": "3",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "1",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "22a963bf-6b05-4663-8001-ba785b339638",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "You cannot destroy a Wraith by simply fighting it. Even if I force it to dissipate, it will just return to its phylactery and hide there. The magic barrier will remain.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "1",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "55658cfd-ee5a-43f0-957d-0165e7585f11",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "I need an Rune of Command to compel the Wraith to drop its spell. Silvia is making one specifically attuned to this particular Wraith. Once I compel the Wraith to drop the barrier, Shawn can rescue Joel while I destroy the Wraith forever.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "1",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "4250a565-b73f-4b1c-89b7-9abc03ee8336",
                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "So we must wait and do nothing while that Wraith slowly drains the life away from Joel?",
                                    "emotion": "3",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "1",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "8f016861-f47a-4076-83f8-45fb2be6af46",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "If I confront the Wraith without the Rune, it is unlikely to fight me. We can't risk it just killing Joel outright from spite. The only reason Joel is still alive now is that he's found some sort of sanctuary.",
                                    "emotion": "2",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "1",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "7580d2b1-793f-4042-a568-ffd922d101c7",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Sometimes, the hardest part of being a hero is not simply doing what is right, but doing what is right the right way.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "1",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "nodes.branchSection",
                            "expression": null,
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "a4782141-5954-4e77-a7a7-8924dbf4f0e2",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Is there some reason why I haven't seen the other teachers here recently? I thought that midterm break was over.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "1",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "29786df7-b0e4-4d0d-9ea4-e7cb56b623af",
                                    "actorId": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "One of the Rogue students be missing. The instructors be searching for him in the Sea Caves. I have a bad feeling in my heart that they will not find him.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "1",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "92356791-e9f1-4b9f-b0ae-b1476336be39",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "A missing student? Great Caesar's Ghost!",
                                    "emotion": "4",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "1",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "8948cbfb-56db-4677-9e8f-4886874b46c6",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "This is a great opportunity for me to test my steam-powered mechanical bloodhound! All I'll need is a sample of the student's blood, his shoe size, and a few strands of his hair.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "1",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "a0998500-dc60-48b0-9bd4-e1c2449b7122",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "text": "As long as the lad is nowhere near the water, my mechanical bloodhound should track him down in a matter of hours!",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "1",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "1fc6a5ba-5ca2-4ab8-990c-8767a9bb04e5",
                                    "actorId": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "The boy be lost in the Sea Caves, Dr. The SEA caves.\n",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "1",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "388aafd1-c009-4af2-be38-d0d2c8a9683a",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Pity. Another Scientific Breakthrough opportunity lost.\n",
                                    "emotion": "2",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "1",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}